## Author last edit: Marc A.T. Teunis (dd 28 July 2018)
## Analytes: ApoE (apoe); PLP (plp); EGCG (egcg) and BBCI (bbci)
## Dataset published in: Head-to-Head Comparison of Anti-Inflammatory Performance of
## Experimental design: Three replicates per group (A, B, and C). Cells were exposed to
## different natural products (natural_product), in triplicates (A1:A3, ...). The outcome
## parameter (the numeric values in the cells) are the measured IL-8 (cytokine) concentration as determined
## by ELISA. For more details see the literature reference above.
